**Masalah:** `useEffect` dengan async IIFE di `TeacherAttendanceForm.tsx:19-31` dan `AttendanceForm.tsx:39-54` tidak punya `AbortController`. Cepat mengganti tanggal → respon sebelumnya bisa menimpa data terbaru.

**Fix — AbortController + ignore flag:**

```tsx
// src/app/teacher/attendance/TeacherAttendanceForm.tsx
useEffect(() => {
  const controller = new AbortController();
  let cancelled = false;

  (async () => {
    setIsLoading(true);
    try {
      const res = await fetch(`/api/teacher/attendance?tanggal=${tanggal}`, {
        signal: controller.signal,
      });
      if (cancelled || res.status === 403) return;
      const d = await res.json();
      if (cancelled) return;
      setStudents((d.students || []).map(...));
      setIsSuccess(!!d.alreadySubmitted);
    } catch { /* ignore */ }
    finally { if (!cancelled) setIsLoading(false); }
  })();

  return () => { cancelled = true; controller.abort(); };
}, [tanggal]);
```

